</span></div><p itemprop="description">外甲所有板件都采用了隐藏式水口。</p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a78z7vol/pic_11/' target='_blank'><img alt="2020最值得入手的高达RG？万代脉冲高达空装版RG拼装实录" src="https://am.zdmimg.com/202008/03/5f28301e332c98786.jpg_e680.jpg" /></a></p><p itemprop="description">先拼出了架核心战机占个位置。</p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a78z7vol/pic_12/' target='_blank'><img alt="2020最值得入手的高达RG？万代脉冲高达空装版RG拼装实录" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202008/03/5f28301e7c0c69600.jpg_e680.jpg" /></a></p><p itemprop="description">感觉这款核心战机跟之前PB限定的炮装脉冲差不多，除了尺寸小点。</p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a78z7vol/pic_13/' target='_blank'><img alt="2020最值得入手的高达RG？万代脉冲高达空装版RG拼装实录" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202008/03/5f28302e50ae67447.jpg_e680.jpg" /></a></p><p itemprop="description">胸甲，用喵匠的软头<a class="seo_link" href="https://www.smzdm.com/fenlei/makebi/" target="_blank">马克笔</a>涂了涂色，很好用，比郡仕的马克笔好用。</p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a78z7vol/pic_14/' target='_blank'><img alt="2020最值得入手的高达RG？万代脉冲高达空装版RG拼装实录" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202008/03/5f28302ea71bf504.jpg_e680.jpg" /></a></p><p itemprop="description">接着拼装双臂，整体连接肩甲，紧致度都很高，不会出现掉件等问题。好评。<img alt="2020最值得入手的高达RG？万代脉冲高达空装版RG拼装实录" src="https://res.smzdm.com/images/emotions/28.png" class="face" /></p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a78z7vol/pic_15/' target='_blank'><img alt="2020最值得入手的高达RG？万代脉冲高达空装版RG拼装实录" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202008/04/5f294271a0de1815.jpg_e680.jpg" /></a></p><p itemprop="description">上半身拼接完成。</p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a78z7vol/pic_16/' target='_blank'><img alt="2020最值得入手的高达RG？万代脉冲高达空装版RG拼装实录" src="https://am.zdmimg.com/202008/04/5f2942726d7311026.jpg_e680.jpg" /></a></p><p itemprop="description">头部，雪铁龙还在，细节还可以。</p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a78z7vol/pic_17/' target='_blank'><img alt="2020最值得入手的高达RG？万代脉冲高达空装版RG拼装实录" src="htt